    "name": "Greenhouse",
    "steam_appid": 3207210,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>进入并逃离园区</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是为了调查而潜入的，但现在你需要逃出去。探索杂草丛生的花园、阴森的走廊、迷宫般的路径和艺术画廊。每进入一个新区域，你的角色会自动拍一张照片。利用相册来追踪你的进度，确保没有遗漏任何重要细节。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207210/extras/1a121580176bce46352930b91085272b.poster.avif?t=1765932610\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207210/extras/1a121580176bce46352930b91085272b.webm?t=1765932610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207210/extras/1a121580176bce46352930b91085272b.mp4?t=1765932610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>揭开谜团</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索这座关闭的游乐园。与物品互动，激发你的第六感，揭示游客，甚至可能是你自己留下的线索和记忆。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207210/extras/66bcf27864bb74e85d569b3c0c0e2b8e.poster.avif?t=1765932610\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207210/extras/66bcf27864bb74e85d569b3c0c0e2b8e.webm?t=1765932610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207210/extras/66bcf27864bb74e85d569b3c0c0e2b8e.mp4?t=1765932610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>解开谜题</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一些谜题会随着每次游戏而变化。利用物理和视角谜题，开辟前进的道路。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207210/extras/542c36f29e182ad0914f183b39a99038.poster.avif?t=1765932610\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207210/extras/542c36f29e182ad0914f183b39a99038.webm?t=1765932610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207210/extras/542c36f29e182ad0914f183b39a99038.mp4?t=1765932610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>沉浸式环境</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一切都被设计得尽可能真实——风的声音、在不同表面上行走的脚步声。水面泛起涟漪，走过时会减缓你的速度。植物在你经过时弯曲和沙沙作响。极简的界面和无缝的场景加载让你始终沉浸在游戏中。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207210/extras/bea4c6361c87e12278c8b3457fe0cb65.poster.avif?t=1765932610\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207210/extras/bea4c6361c87e12278c8b3457fe0cb65.webm?t=1765932610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207210/extras/bea4c6361c87e12278c8b3457fe0cb65.mp4?t=1765932610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>改变天气</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >捡起雨伞或太阳镜来改变天气。你可以选择下雨或晴天，以适应你想要的氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207210/extras/b143e84150e3581956266505f1289fe7.poster.avif?t=1765932610\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207210/extras/b143e84150e3581956266505f1289fe7.webm?t=1765932610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207210/extras/b143e84150e3581956266505f1289fe7.mp4?t=1765932610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>作为散步模拟还是与怪物对抗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择一个安静的、令人毛骨悚然的散步体验，或者逐个开启不同的怪物类型和跳跃惊吓，提升恐怖感。使用杀虫喷雾来抵御毒虫。如果你遇到园丁……赶紧逃命！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207210/extras/ad7efff8aab615836730a30526ee2d37.poster.avif?t=1765932610\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207210/extras/ad7efff8aab615836730a30526ee2d37.webm?t=1765932610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207210/extras/ad7efff8aab615836730a30526ee2d37.mp4?t=1765932610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
